import React from 'react'; import Title from '../Title/Title'; import styled from "styled-components"; export default function ExecutiveDiv({name,subHeading,content,contactName,emailId,mobileNumber}){ return(
<Title name={subHeading} fontSize={"24px"} fontFamily={"Montserrat-Bold"} color={"#404040"} /> <p className="pt-40"> {content} </p> </div> </div> </div> <div className="col-4 col-lg-4 pt-90"> <p className="pt-50">{contactName}</p> <p><a href="tel:">{mobileNumber}</a> </p> <p><a href="mailto:johndoe@csrx.org">{emailId}</a> </p> </div> </div> </div> ) }
